FitNFoot is a modern and responsive web application developed for showcasing fitness and footwear collections. The project focuses on promoting an active and healthy lifestyle while providing users with a simple and engaging interface. It is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript with Node.js tools for better performance and scalability. The design is fully responsive, ensuring smooth usability across desktops, tablets, and mobile devices. The application highlights stylish footwear options and integrates clean layouts with interactive elements to enhance user experience. Overall, FitNFoot combines functionality with modern design principles to create a professional and user-friendly platform.
